text: Charles Patrick (13 January 1866 - 29 November 1919) was an Australian cricketer. He played six first-class matches for New South Wales and Queensland between 1893/94 and 1903/04. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1866 births Category:1919 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Queensland cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
